Class Feedback

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.webcat.deveventtracker.models.Feedback

  • public class Feedback
extends Object
    Represents an assignment state for a given student. Encapsulates current file sizes, the assignment offering for this project, and incremental development metrics.

    2018-09-13
    Author:

      • processBatch

        public Map<String,Long> processBatch(List<SensorData> events)
        Given a set of SensorData events, return the total number of edits and the total number of weighted edits contained in those events. Edits are weighted by time, i.e., the number of days until the assignment deadline.
        Parameters:
        events - An array of SensorData events
        Returns:
        A HashMap<String, Long> containing the keys totalEdits, totalWeightedEdits, and lastUpdated
        See Also:
        EarlyOften
